Package: context
Type: Package
Title: Manages metadata about projects composed of code and manuscripts.
Version: 1.0
Date: 2015-06-26
Author: Krzysztof Sakrejda
Maintainer: Krzysztof Sakrejda <krzysztof.sakrejda@gmail.com>
Description: Keep a hierarchical definition of project metadata such as libraries used, git hashes, and locations of data/input/output in a single unified JSON file.
License: GPL-2
Depends: jsonlite, magrittr, igraph
